On the last page that she's a Super Saiyan in, the square text box says something along the lines of "Even after all that was over, I went and did something crazy" or something "fucked up". And in the last page where she's kissing him, she basically says "I'm gonna keep training with you like this from now on." the second text bubble with the heart says "Old man" or "Senpai". The bottom right text bubble is Goku asking her what she just did with sticking her mouth on his, and the other bubble has her saying "You don't know? But you have children... That was just a kiss".

And that's it for the most part. I'd post the translated pages but really it's too rough of a translation since Google Translate REALLY butchered some things and it took my knowledge of the characters to piece together what a lot of the text bubbles/boxes were saying.

On that same page as she goes SSJ2, she says something like "But I'm feeling something else strange, it's too good to be true" or "This is too good to be training" or "This fighting is too good" or something along that gist. On page 11, Caulifla comments on her head feeling strange, saying something like "Hey, wait a minute..." and "Wait... slow down a little...". The next page I'm not sure if she's talking out loud or in her head, but she basically says "Though yeah, I do wanna get stronger, but... I'm gonna bear his child" and in the square box it either says "What are you saying?" or "What am I saying?" because I'm not sure who's talking. The next one I'm pretty sure is in her head as she's like "He and I will definitely have a strong child for sure" and in the second square box it says "But... I feel like I want it". And then she basically gives up fighting it and saying she can't think anymore and just wants him to keep stretching her, & he says something like "You got it, Cauli"

On the same page at the end, she says something like "I can tell I'll overpower you if I squeeze like this", and on the next page I think makes a comment about Goku's dick hitting her deeper than she expected or hitting her somewhere unfamiliar, and Goku saying how good it feels. Then I think on the next page it's saying Caulifla's body is moving on its own, and Caulifla goes "Such an intense fight. He's thrusting so hard..." but inside being like "I am a Saiyan. I'm not going to lose!" (this may have been Goku thinking it) But then he goes Ultra Instinct and Caulifla's like "That's...! But why now..!?" And he begins to overpower her, and she's like "I don't know what to do, but I feel his -power- inside me!" Then she goes Super Saiyan 2, and this part is rough & Idk who's exactly talking, but it's basically saying "A Super Saiyan should be able to handle it" and talk about "That familiar sensation in my back is back" & "I might get stronger" implying that his power's flowing into her

Hoping this gets a translation soon. I was only able to do so much with Google Translate. The gist is it saying Goku revived everyone with the Super Dragon Balls with the Zen-oh twins saying to do it again sometime, and that Caulifla went to Universe 7 as Goku's disciple. They're then in the Hyperbolic Time Chamber and I believe Caulifla talks about doing some "special training" with Goku, citing "A Saiyan woman can grow stronger if she does it with a strong man", with an asterisk that says 'I'm actually not sure' after Goku's like "Really? Then let's try it". She says outwardly "Don't get me wrong, this is only to get stronger!" but inside she's like "Why am I doing this...". The whole time, she treats Goku like her opponent with this "training", but begins to feel strange. That's when she gets in his face and goes "Come on, senpai" (it translated as Old Man, but I like senpai better) and puts him inside of her in order to gain the advantage and "win the battle" on page 6.
